{"tid":1802272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[姐妹不和] 姐姐指被妹妹看不起，要問責都未輪到你","createTime":"2019-12-29T10:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T11:06:48.000Z","uid":271049,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"741e8f816607456f3db98664aaa1f52d957f8e9c","tid":1802272,"uid":271049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"葉劉：暫緩修例感「被跣」　有行會成員曾提出總辭　林鄭指問責未輪到行會<br />\n立場報道2019/12/29 &mdash; 17:43<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年6月特首林鄭月娥宣布暫緩修訂逃犯條例，有傳林鄭當時曾多次向建制派致歉。行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀近日接受《有線新聞》專訪時，坦言政府曾向她表明不會退讓，及後卻宣布暫緩修例，令她感到「被跣」。她又指行會成員曾提出總辭，但林鄭卻認為行會角色「邊緣」毋須問責辭職。<br />\n<br />\n有線今日播出葉劉淑儀專訪，她指曾經就修例工作致電政府，而對方表明不會退讓。之後政府卻決定暫緩修例工作，林鄭在作正式宣布前有見她解釋原因，「那我知道我『被跣』了」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀指行會成員曾經提議總辭，但林鄭認為問責亦未輪到行會：「我們有個別成員socially（社交上）見到特首都會講，我們不介意，如果總辭幫到你。如果要辭就總辭，集體負責嘛。但行政長官說行會角色是『邊緣』，只是給予意見，要問責幾時輪到行會成員。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRZ56et.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRZ56et.png&h=e2e79002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被問到司、局長又應否問責，葉劉回應稱：「高層官員的改組，能否幫到件事呢？如果有可能幫到的，唔係淨係話問責，等市民消氣。我諗其實好多問責的班子，這幾個月咁辛苦，佢哋係咪真係咁戀棧呢？我都唔知、唔懷疑，不過在政府角度，如果不讓他們走，要考慮的是找甚麼人去填補。」至於最應問責的官員是哪一位？葉劉稱：「我唔方便講。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E6%84%9F-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B7%A3-%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%9B%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%8C%87%E5%95%8F%E8%B2%AC%E6%9C%AA%E8%BC%AA%E5%88%B0%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%2584%259F-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B7%25A3-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9y3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=dcc4cca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%2584%259F-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B7%25A3-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2595%258F%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=339ea69f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E6%84%9F-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B7%A3-%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E6%9B%BE%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%8C%87%E5%95%8F%E8%B2%AC%E6%9C%AA%E8%BC%AA%E5%88%B0%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18dd4662ee8156a6889b58eaa3b4e4cd9f9679c","tid":1802272,"uid":22719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"真係要隊左草先整到張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e97163f13e80eefdffe7c65142ca9ef964a0c59","tid":1802272,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e18dd4662ee8156a6889b58eaa3b4e4cd9f9679c","tid":1802272,"uid":22719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"真係要隊左草先整到張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"抽提子要有咩腦沖擊先會咁樣放法?<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/29/LWnhf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F29%2FLWnhf1.png&h=d1602eb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1e49d918001faeebf67132472fb8bddf8aec2",